ComicInfo.Summary: Katchoo's dreams are still uneasy and the ghost of Emma looms large in her subconscious. She finally takes a call from David and buries herself in her artworks. Francie has a bad day bumping into Freddie and fiancee, the bubbly and lithe, Casey. Feeling inadequate she buys a more sexy dress much to Katchoo's surprise and delight. Meanwhile a badly beaten Digman is left at a hospital where his facial injuries remind Detective Walsh of how Katchoo handled herself when she was in custody, giving him cause to issue a warrant for her arrest for questioning.
ComicInfo.Title: Something I Can't Hear
